'''Gijan''' ({{lang-fa|<U+06AF><U+064A><U+062C><U+0627><U+0646>}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''G<U+012B>j<U+0101>n'''; also known as '''K<U+012B>j<U+0101>n''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|-3841777|Gijan}}</ref> is a village in [[Kuhestan Rural District (Chalus County)|Kuhestan Rural District]], [[Kelardasht District]], [[Chalus County]], [[Mazandaran Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 91, in 24 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|02}}</ref>  

